'From Cuis 2.3 of 22 March 2010 [latest update: #472] on 18 April 2010 at 10:42:46 pm'!!Object methodsFor: 'printing' stamp: 'jmv 4/18/2010 22:41'!fullPrintString	"Answer a String whose characters are a description of the receiver."	^String streamContents: [ :s | self printOn: s]! !!MethodNode methodsFor: 'converting' stamp: 'jmv 4/18/2010 22:41'!decompileString 	"Answer a string description of the parse tree whose root is the receiver."	"Unfortunately, #pringString limits the result."	^self fullPrintString! !